{
  "stem": "26983.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a very famous painter of the ghetto, Professor Otto Ungar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he gave me private lessons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What does it mean, private lessons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even before.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even before the deportation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in Ostrava, when things became bad and we knew the deportation is very near, Leo Haas, the famous painter from the ghettos, he was living near Mahrisch Ostrau.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then he came to Mahrisch Ostrau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he gave me his first lessons in drawing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later on, he gave me also-- he had for a child of 13, 14, to encourage me in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And later, I got private lessons also from a Fleischmann.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Fleischmann was the head of the-- we would call it, like, minister of hells.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he was a doctor, an artist, and a writer and a poet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he showed me his office that was in a special room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After the work, I could come to him, show him my work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He criticized it and helped me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was Fleischmann.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Fritta I met at Edelstein's.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And these were most of them the artists of Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because this artist worked in the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was a special unit who prepared drawings and illustrations for the camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, for the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How you would call it for-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, they had to give a [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A kind of a report for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this has to be done in a special way that is suitable for the German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was also Spero, I think, a Dutch painter with some very sweet drawings for these Germans, and who also designed stamps--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was a [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
